{"tid":1036861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港島總區行動部 誠信貼紙設計比賽 亞軍隊伍的休班警員麥潤森 涉扶手電梯手機偷拍裙底","createTime":"2019-02-25T13:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T16:02:19.000Z","uid":214534,"like":83,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"44b95a937e08f931e038ad4fdcc1267d32a40018","tid":1036861,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">涉扶手電梯手機偷拍裙底 休班警被控有違公德行為罪<br />\n<br />\n休班警涉於金鐘海富中心扶手電梯上，以手機偷拍女途人裙底，被控有違公德行為罪，案件今（25日）於東區裁判法院提堂。被告暫時毋須答辯，押後至4月8日再訊，被告准以500元保釋候訊。<br />\n<br />\n被告麥潤森（36歲），報稱職業警員，被控於2018年12月18日，在金鐘夏愨道18號海富中心3號扶手電梯，作出性質猥褻、淫褻及令人憎惡的有違公德行為，即使用手提電話偷影女子X裙底。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2279493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2279493&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8VUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=ffa926ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2279493</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港島總區行動部初級警務人員誠信管理委員會於去年十二月舉辦「誠信擋風玻璃行車證貼紙設計比賽2017」，藉此提醒各警務人員要恪守誠信，拒絕各種有違誠信價值觀的誘惑。</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1107/chi/6467.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1107%2Fchi%2F6467.html&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8VUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=32bd0ba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1107/chi/6467.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1107/images/20180320_a27b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1107%2Fimages%2F20180320_a27b1.jpg&h=12f3dd73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左一、左二、右一<br />\n我呢三位係警員，唔知邊位係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">疑犯</span>？"},{"pid":"536ce2d3ab0a6c5ec8710436df09dae3c3e8b261","tid":1036861,"uid":214534,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T13:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f388bc46f73e8565df286a20cf73fa07e2af70","tid":1036861,"uid":48234,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">誠信?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e5252cc922b90daffe2a522196969770703c88","tid":1036861,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2f388bc46f73e8565df286a20cf73fa07e2af70","tid":1036861,"uid":48234,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">誠信?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_combo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aee95dc0666560254c4661378f44504861410c1","tid":1036861,"uid":130695,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T13:52:40.000Z","msg":"香港警察 十個有九個都..<br />\n算啦 我想讚都讚唔出口<br />\n幫大陸狗打壓良民 欺善怕惡<br />\n警黑合作，對香港人兇狠對大陸閪碌撚<br />\n對鬼佬爭住含"},{"pid":"3fa61408aa9f4e513fd6cc3a81f0d82a129c4f22","tid":1036861,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d199bb466d77105ba54dc5cf1fe0938cac5120","tid":1036861,"uid":191919,"like":4,"dislike":46,"score":-42,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f894d4ed7528b2a15254be2bbd5915e74fc9f78","tid":1036861,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"c5d199bb466d77105ba54dc5cf1fe0938cac5120","tid":1036861,"uid":191919,"like":4,"dislike":46,"score":-42,"citedBy":6,